tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review: I have consulted Dr. Neena on many occasions for both my daughters' health. She is very efficient and does not give medicines unless really needed which is something I really appreciate. She believes strongly in allowing kids' immune system to learn by itself before giving medicines. My kids fall sick much less often now as I follow her advise on their nutrition as well! All in all I strongly recommend Dr. Neena to all my friends and family.

Very good at her work, lots of patiences. Listens carefully to  issues and addresses them quickly. She is also very friendly and available during non working hours incase of any emergency, would definitely recommend her. Grateful to know her üòä

What I appreciate most about her is her conservative approach to prescribing medications ‚Äì *** ***** ***** ** ************ **************
